# API origin the BFF proxies to (server-side only; never exposed to the browser).
# Local dev: the FastAPI service (uvicorn) on port 8000.
# Production: the deployed API URL, e.g. https://community-energy-flex-api.fly.dev
# Without it, the app falls back to http://127.0.0.1:8000 and the pages show a
# "data service unavailable" notice instead of crashing.
API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
